highlights.text: Padam Kadala by Sagar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hyderabad, up 31 spots at #57.
Chitti (From "Jathi Ratnalu") by Ram Miriyala and Radhan has been on Top Songs Hyderabad the longest, at 54 weeks straight.
Sid Sriram has the most spots on Top Songs Hyderabad. Kumkumala (From "Brahmastra (Telugu)") is the highest at #6.
Chukkala Chunni by Anurag Kulkarni and Chaitan Bharadwaj is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hyderabad at #32.
